{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7829064093","title":"川西区党委有关镇反的简报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0a08cef24a","index":0,"year":1951,"month":10,"day":24,"articleId":"7829064093"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b44ed8323b","type":"title","text":"川西区党委有关镇反的简报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7829064093"},{"id":"e6fd725271","type":"paragraph","text":"9月20日至10月20日一月内全区所判死刑、死刑缓期二年执行及无期徒刑之数字及总数简报。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7829064093"},{"id":"876dffef99","type":"paragraph","text":"一、全区土改乡一月内批准了死刑10名，连前共561名（因已批超过数字，现已由各地退回，故比上次少了39名）。其中：特务21名，匪首173名，政匪100名，惯匪36名，恶霸203名，有破坏行为之一贯道首7，其他反革命犯21。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7829064093"},{"id":"81d050a57d","type":"paragraph","text":"二、全区土改乡一月内批准死刑缓期二年执行54名，连前共301名。其中特务11名，匪首52名，政匪112名，惯匪18名，恶霸79名，有破坏行为之一贯道首4名，其他反革命犯25名。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7829064093"},{"id":"c2fdb4f7cf","type":"paragraph","text":"三、成都市在本月内未判处。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7829064093"},{"id":"ca1c0b6b9c","type":"paragraph","text":"四、全区一月内批准无期徒刑59名，连前共373名，其中特务46名，匪首43名，政匪192名，恶霸33名，惯匪15名，其他反革命犯44。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7829064093"},{"id":"355b847508","type":"paragraph","text":" 川西区党委10月24日","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7829064093"}],"page":{"id":"0f2c5f557b","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7829064093","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}